Sial.

528
00:46:22,066 --> 00:46:23,300
Halo.

529
00:46:32,366 --> 00:46:34,933
Kuharap leluhurmu sedang menyaksikan.

530
00:47:06,000 --> 00:47:09,400
Sejujurnya, aku tak merasa senang
