540
00:49:21,833 --> 00:49:25,766
Mengapa?
/ Temanmu sudah mengampuni satu petarung kami.

541
00:49:27,166 --> 00:49:28,166
Sekarang kita impas.

542
00:49:29,033 --> 00:49:30,066
Omong-omong,

543
00:49:31,066 --> 00:49:32,066
