568
00:54:55,966 --> 00:54:57,666
Dia menanyakan dirimu.

569
00:54:59,433 --> 00:55:00,233
Liu Kang.

570
00:55:07,766 --> 00:55:08,566
Putraku.

571
00:55:19,266 --> 00:55:20,533
Apa yang terjadi?

572
00:55:23,233 --> 00:55:24,566
Aku bunuh dia.

573
00:55:25,166 --> 00:55:26,733
Aku tak punya pilihan.

574
00:55:27,466 --> 00:55:28,800
Maafkan aku.

575
00:55:32,833 --> 00:55:33,666
Di mana Cole?

576
00:55:35,966 --> 00:55:37,600
Dia tidak kembali?

577
00:55:40,666 --> 00:55:42,133
Oh, sial.

578
00:55:53,757 --> 00:55:55,757
Penyihir,

579
00:55:56,200 --> 00:55:58,266
