664
01:02:22,833 --> 01:02:24,766
Ya, setuju sekali, sangat setuju.

665
01:02:26,100 --> 01:02:27,200
Sebentar, bro.

666
01:02:27,224 --> 01:02:28,199
Teman-teman,

667
01:02:28,200 --> 01:02:30,000
