668
01:02:30,024 --> 01:02:32,324
Aku... aku tak sanggup lakukan ini.
/ Tak mungkin.

669
01:02:33,833 --> 01:02:34,633
Cukup!

670
01:02:35,366 --> 01:02:36,400
Kita bertarung!

671
01:02:37,000 --> 01:02:37,766
Whoa, bentar.

672
01:02:37,766 --> 01:02:41,133
Tentukan aturannya dulu,
jangan pukul muka.

673
01:03:02,566 --> 01:03:04,966
Senjata! Aku butuh senjata!

674
01:03:07,990 --> 01:03:09,390
Waduh!

675
01:03:43,000 --> 01:03:44,266
Oh, yang benar saja?

676
01:04:31,300 --> 01:04:32,700
Sekarang, jangan berdiri!

677
01:04:36,066 --> 01:04:37,000
Oh, gawat.

678
01:04:52,166 --> 01:04:54,900
Ini cara yang sangat bodoh untuk kalah.

679
01:04:54,924 --> 01:04:56,299
Ayo lekas, berdiri.

680
01:04:57,033 --> 01:04:57,833
Berdiri.

681
01:05:16,300 --> 01:05:18,700
Kamu seorang aktor,
jadi beraktinglah.

682
01:05:23,633 --> 01:05:25,333
Baiklah, monster jelek.

683
01:05:30,566 --> 01:05:32,166
Saatnya pertunjukan!

684
01:06:02,990 --> 01:06:03,990
Ayo.

685
01:06:40,914 --> 01:06:41,814
Ooh!

686
01:06:41,866 --> 01:06:43,700
Mantap!

687
01:06:52,924 --> 01:06:54,324
Itu...

688
01:06:54,566 --> 01:06:57,266
